  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 2 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}That's not important. Why didn't you call off the operation?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 2 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}Is your mission worth your life?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 2 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}Dying is what people fear the most...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 2 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}Is it not?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}Well... I've never actually given anyone orders before.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}They wouldn't listen to me, even if I tried...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Y'see, uh... I'm not really the one in charge...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}So, you were lying earlier?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Why...?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}I don't understand.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}Hey... Can you tell me one thing? Was it all... just an act?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 18 0 0}...?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
