  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}The way we met at the station, that cut on your hand, the drawings... Were you just setting me up?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}Now that I think about it, a real cut wouldn't have disappeared that fast...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}Haha... I see how it is...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
