  <Dialog id="27" name="MSG_026_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0007"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 3 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 36 0 0}I... I didn't even sense her until now... This is the only thing I can do, and yet...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
