    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 222 6 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 38 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 6 25 25}I certainly didn't have the slightest clue she was here...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
