    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 222 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 46 0 0}I'll go ahead and arrange a hospital room for her. She'll have to be placed under watch, but I'm sure she understands.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
